#: src/qml/Settings/AudioSettings.qml:153
msgctxt "@info:tooltip"
msgid ""
"Adjust volume gain according to <i>replaygain</i> values stored in the file "
"metadata. If set to album gain, apply album gain if present and fallback to "
"track gain otherwise."
